item.title: Please join the viking village.
item.content:encoded: The Viking village is a great place with people who like to talk. More talkative then alot of villages and has great people who like to help.Plus occasionally we have contests. If you join say Myusha sent ya XD That and if you do it I'llowe ya a favor :)
